# Practice Levels

#### Practice levels are the final levels in most lessons. They let students apply lesson knowledge and develop fluency in new concepts and syntax. 

#### The difficulty of the levels progress, meaning, level A is the easiest to complete, while C or D will be more challenging. 

#### Students can choose which levels to complete and don't need to finish all before moving on.

